## Known Selectors (BoardBots)

Use these selectors for Cmux ad-hoc testing and Playwright tests:

### Landing Page
- Register button: `#btn-register`
- Login button: `#btn-login`

### Auth Modal
- Username input: `#auth-username`
- Password input: `#auth-password`
- Confirm password: `#auth-confirm`
- Submit button: `#submit-btn`
- Modal container: `.login-modal`

### Dashboard
- Container: `.dashboard-container`
- New game button: `#btn-new-game`
- Logout button: `#btn-logout`

### Lobby
- Container: `.lobby-container`
- Game name input: `#game-name`
- Create game button: `#btn-create`
- Start game button: `#btn-start-game`
- Waiting text: "Waiting for players"

### Game
- Canvas element: `#game-canvas`
- Turn indicator: `.turn-indicator`
- Robot placement: Click canvas at coordinates

